  "type": "written",
  "marks": 2,
  "num": "Q3",
  "question": "<p>State the most suitable data type for each of the following pieces of data.</p><p>(a) A person's shoe size, e.g. 8  <strong>[1]</strong><br>(b) The average speed of a car in mph, e.g. 62.4  <strong>[1]</strong></p>",
