  "num": "Q6",
  "question": "<p>The following algorithm runs.</p><pre>function square(n)\n  return n * n\nendfunction\n\ntotal = 0\nfor i = 1 to 4\n  total = total + square(i)\nnext i\nprint(total)</pre><p>Complete the trace table to show the value of <strong>square(i)</strong> and the running value of <strong>total</strong> after each pass of the loop.</p>",
