   "markScheme": "<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>Mark Scheme — 4 marks (1 mark per correct row of the trace)</h5>\n<ul>\n<li>Pass 1 → i = 1, square(i) = 1, total = 1</li>\n<li>Pass 2 → i = 2, square(i) = 4, total = 5</li>\n<li>Pass 3 → i = 3, square(i) = 9, total = 14</li>\n<li>Pass 4 → i = 4, square(i) = 16, total = 30</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"marks-section\">\n<h5>How the marks are given</h5>\n<ul><li>1 mark for each fully-correct row. The program finally outputs 30.</li></ul>\n</div>",
