  "question": "<p>The following code runs.</p><pre>procedure setDiscount(amount)\n  discount = amount * 0.1\n  print(discount)\nendprocedure\n\nsetDiscount(200)\nprint(discount)</pre><p>State what is printed by the <strong>first</strong> print(discount), inside the procedure, and explain why the <strong>second</strong> print(discount) causes an error.</p>",
