  "question": "<p>A program accepts a whole number quiz score from <strong>0 to 20</strong>. Tick <strong>one</strong> box in each row to classify the test data.</p>",
  "format": "tickGrid",
  "hint": "Check the type first (text = erroneous); if it's a whole number, check whether it's typical, at an edge, or outside 0–20.",
