  "source": "exam",
  "type": "written",
  "marks": 8,
  "num": "Q12",
  "question": "<p>A program asks the user to enter a whole number number of students going on a trip. It should accept any whole number from <strong>1 to 30</strong>.</p><p>Create a test plan for this input. Choose <strong>one</strong> suitable value for each of the four types of test data (normal, boundary, invalid, erroneous), and state the expected result for each.</p>",
