  "num": "Q12",
  "question": "<p>Give <strong>two</strong> reasons why a programmer might choose to write a small embedded system's control software in a low-level language rather than a high-level language.</p>",
  "hint": "Think about how much memory a small embedded device usually has, and how directly the software needs to control the hardware.",
